OL,5, UK-based carmaker Mini has responded to
OL,6, an internet uproar in China accusing it
OL,7, of racism at the Shanghai Auto Show.   
OL,9,FA video from the event appeared to show
OL,10,FMini staff offering ice cream to       
OL,11,Fforeigners while refusing to give it to
OL,12,FChinese visitors.                      
OL,14,FMini China, which is owned by Germany's
OL,15,FBMW, said the workers were distributing
OL,16,Fthe treats to company employees.       
OL,18,FHowever, it also said that it was      
OL,19,F"deeply sorry for the negative mood the
OL,20,Fincident brought on everyone".         
